{"tid":603090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[財爺派4000蚊] 大學生:旅行四千元去得哪?去長洲嗎? 四千元電話都買不了一部!","createTime":"2018-03-23T12:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T13:36:12.000Z","uid":34550,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"828aa51b89920b2292cc031376fab5ee24b8784a","tid":603090,"uid":34550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/202254_fe07eee1f0268775c646e844b05bff2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F202254_fe07eee1f0268775c646e844b05bff2d.png&h=295d61ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/202254_d9b6f4554ead74cebd62effb6a671a52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F202254_d9b6f4554ead74cebd62effb6a671a52.png&h=80251cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/202254_9a11768d2c2eea7c331011b06a7d4eb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F202254_9a11768d2c2eea7c331011b06a7d4eb2.png&h=9d64f3b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有大學生認為派四千不足夠<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】今次派四千元，很多大學生受惠，有大學生認為派四千元太少，亦有市民覺得有錢派已滿足。有學者指，今次方案涉及不同派錢條件，行政費會相當高。<br />\n<br />\n今次補漏方案有不少條件限制，計算及審查方法亦較複雜。<br />\n<br />\n我們以一對領取高齡津貼的夫婦為例，在預算案中出三糧，各人可額外獲得2690元，在補漏方案中每人可以獲發1310元的差額。不過如果他們其中一人持有物業，假設有三千元差餉寬免，這樣他就不符合資格。<br />\n<br />\n另一例子是一名打工仔要交一千元薪俸稅，在預算案中他可以獲750元退稅，而他同時持有物業，可以拿到三千元差餉寬免，這樣在新方案中，他隻可以拿到250元。<br />\n<br />\n今次派四千元很多大學生受惠，有大學生認為派四千元不足夠，亦有市民覺得有錢派已滿足。<br />\n<br />\n有學者指，今次方案涉及不同派錢條件，行政費會相當高，又指這是一個政治問題，以全民派錢來解決更直接。<br />\n<br />\n政府在2011年曾經試過向全港市民派發六千元，當年三月宣布措施之後分批接受市民登記，首批要十月尾才收到款項。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/editorsChoice/player?newsId=258480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D258480&d=UMigsLiDAYQDA6SGr28idi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e8dec627\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D258480&h=e9d6bb1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/editorsChoice/player?newsId=258480</a>"},{"pid":"9244c1e5e4225dddcd11d7434478b45edd11b6ed","tid":603090,"uid":16880,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:25:55.000Z","msg":"西面港女"},{"pid":"fa5c41854fde5fa19017ab4958aaa5792e769080","tid":603090,"uid":77196,"like":13,"dislike":20,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"咁撚臭串，應該在學學生冇份，反正班大學生都對社會冇乜貢獻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a189edc91727ae8edc93e21e0bbf5bd55305c1","tid":603090,"uid":16676,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:38:51.000Z","msg":"反而MPF 對衝<br />\n全民退保<br />\n勞工假呢d 實事又唔去做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3d84ac5b8bb61a2327fbc39435438db080fef35","tid":603090,"uid":1694,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:39:58.000Z","msg":"依啲死撚咗去好過啦，有錢收仲多多聲"},{"pid":"bbd402f8491d4f78fcb95c89f3b1a97a1b259284","tid":603090,"uid":13724,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"屌你老母大學生已經攞緊政府funding讀大學仲咁講嘢"},{"pid":"b439689f80f34f6eb197cb856516812817dabe57","tid":603090,"uid":76776,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:42:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b6741dbe5c49681fd5bf9d35d2be8ae49218c06","tid":603090,"uid":32699,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"佢閪面閪得我好撚開心WO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我開新聞睇閪撚左